Summary: Pydentity is a small web application that manage apache password file (htpasswd) with a simple browser.
License: GNU AGPL v3
Description: Pydentity is a small web application that manage apache password file (htpasswd) with a simple browser.
        
        Current features are:
        
        - change your password by providing the previous one
        - change other people password when you belongs the a specified admin group
        - manage user groups
        - handle authentication through http basic authentication (of course)
Keywords: htpasswd apache web password
Requires: Flask
